{"about_the_game":"In Residuum, players take on the role of a team of miners on Mars, tasked with defending their base from unexpected invaders. With a combination of tower defense and shooter gameplay, players will build structures and mine resources to upgrade their weapons and crew. Each game session lasts 20-30 minutes and players can earn rewards that they can use to upgrade their base in between games.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith a futuristic setting and a variety of enemy types, players will need to use strategy and quick thinking to survive. The addition of unique crew members with special abilities adds another layer of depth to the game, allowing players to choose their team and tailor their strategy to each game session.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nResiduum is a thrilling and fast-paced experience, perfect for players looking for a challenging and rewarding tower defense game. So grab a friend and get ready to defend your base on the Red Planet!","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1463320?t=1739351729","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463320/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739351729","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463320/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739351729","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1463320/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739351729","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"In Residuum, players take on the role of a team of miners on Mars, tasked with defending their base from unexpected invaders. With a combination of tower defense and shooter gameplay, players will build structures and mine resources to upgrade their weapons and crew. Each game session lasts 20-30 minutes and players can earn rewards that they can use to